						<summary>

						<p>On a slab lying in the Jain Basti.</p>						

						<p>1267 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Śaka 1189, Prabhava, Chaitra ba. 4, Tuesday, corresponding to 1267 A.D., March 15.</p>						

						<p>It records the death by <hi rend="italic">Samādhi</hi> of Keḷadi-avve, wife of Vīrayya who was the son of Nōmpiseṭṭi, lay-disciple of Sōmadēvāchārya of <hi rend="italic">Mūla-saṁgha</hi> and <hi rend="italic">Koṇḍakund-ānvaya.</hi></p>						

